==English==
===Etymology===
From [[sym-]] "together" + [[phone]] "sound"

===Adjective===
'''symphonious'''

# Of or pertaining to [[simultaneous]] [[sound]]s that are [[harmonious]] together.
#: ''The '''symphonious''' sound of the fifty skilled musicians was filled the concert hall.''

